window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Shanaya walked into the bar alone, little did she know what pleasures lay in store for her that night. </p> <p>Shanaya was always a bit hesitant about getting too friendly with a stranger at a bar. However, she could not stop herself from getting drawn into the passionate eyes of the mysterious stranger she met that night. </p> <p>Rohan, the sexy stranger, holds the promise of untold pleasures in those deep eyes of his, as he teases her all night long. </p> <p>Will Shanaya be able to prove her dominance in the <i>Games People Play</i> or will she succumb before Rohan?</p>"; 
